Φ(Mythworks) = β(narrative|possibility) ∘ ρ(resonance|emotion) ∘ ✶(framework|complexity) + ε | :generative

β(narrative|possibility): The branching story that generates new possibilities; Wood as experimental apparatus.

ρ(resonance|emotion): The felt truth that fiction accesses; the emotional current beneath literal meaning.

✶(framework|complexity): The harmonic integration where system meets meat; theory encountering blood.

ε: The uncertainty of extrapolation. Does OstrichTech really map to Amazon? Or is that projection?

:state = generative

# Dialectical Pairs
- narrative|possibility: Story as generative engine
- resonance|emotion: Felt truth beneath literal meaning
- framework|complexity: System meeting meat
